                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">General <persName type="from">Lee</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Day</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Havana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-01-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 27, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Just visited General Parrado, Acting Governor-General, with Sigsbee and two of
                    his officers. We were most cordially received, and Parrado returns visit by
                    going aboard <hi rend="italic">Maine</hi> to-morrow.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
